data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
Other applications can lock files temporary e.g. "Backup and Sync from Google" and "OneDrive". It's recommended to turn off file sync temporary to avoid this issue, this will also avoid OneDrice to create duplicate files with names as filename-COMPUTER NAME.ext
- Wait or click "Retry" to check if file is unlocked. - Ignor will try read/write to locked file and cause problem
